What's going on?

13:30.060 --> 13:32.260
再见  乔纳森
Good-bye, Jonathan.

14:13.590 --> 14:15.580
不是这里
This isn't the place.

14:15.590 --> 14:16.780
我用假手都能开那种锁
I could pick that lock with my stump.

14:16.790 --> 14:18.980
不  不
No, n-no, n-no.

14:18.990 --> 14:22.380
这就叫表里不一
Remember what they say about books and their covers.

14:22.390 --> 14:24.180
海瑞·温斯顿把希望之星
When Harry Winston donated the hope diamond

14:24.190 --> 14:26.550
