It's the safest way to go.

14:32.020 --> 14:33.810
毕竟  没人会去邮局
After all, who is going to be looking

14:33.820 --> 14:37.010
查找希望之星
For the hope diamond at the post office, right?

14:37.020 --> 14:39.380
又有谁会到小哈瓦那
And who would be looking for scylla

14:39.390 --> 14:40.980
的一个破烂教堂
At some run-down storefront church

14:40.990 --> 14:43.310
-找"锡拉"呢  -就算你说得对
- In little havana?- All right, let's say you're right.

14:43.320 --> 14:45.210
他们把"锡拉"放里面了
They got scylla back there somewhere.

14:45.220 --> 14:47.810
你进去跟臭保安拼命
You walk in there, reeking that cop stink,

14:47.820 --> 14:49.110
坚持不了多久
You won't last a second.

14:49.120 --> 14:51.980
说得对
That's a good point.

14:51.990 --> 14:53.760
所以由你去
That's why you're going in.

15:08.920 --> 15:11.310
能帮您什么吗
May i help you?

15:11.320 --> 15:13.080
是的  事实上
Yes, as a matter of fact.

15:13.090 --> 15:15.050
我是查尔斯·帕特西
I'm Charles Patoshik.

15:15.060 --> 15:17.310
我是南福罗里达大学的
I'm a professor of anthropology

15:17.320 --> 15:19.180
人类学教授
At southern florida university.

15:19.190 --> 15:21.950
我正在研究不同种类的
I'm doing some various research on various different kinds

15:21.960 --> 15:25.050
加勒比宗教
Of, uh, uh, uh, caribbean religions, and, uh...

15:25.060 --> 15:26.310
或许可以
Perhaps you could start

15:26.320 --> 15:30.290
从里面开始
Back there where you, you do your, uh, services.

15:30.920 --> 15:33.180
那是我们的圣堂
That is our sanctuary.

15:33.190 --> 15:36.650
只有纯洁的心灵 方可进入
Only the pure of soul May venture inside.

15:36.660 --> 15:37.650
了解
I know.

15:37.660 --> 15:40.080
我去过很多圣堂
I-i have been in many such rooms.

15:40.090 --> 15:43.690
让我看看你的手
Let me see your hand.

15:56.190 --> 15:58.410
你心灵不纯
Your soul is black,

15:58.420 --> 16:02.010
沾有无辜人的鲜血
Stained with the blood of the innocent.

16:02.020 --> 16:03.850
我不能让你进去
I cannot let you pass.

16:03.860 --> 16:08.790
从来没有人这么冒犯过我
I have never been so offended in my life.

16:12.920 --> 16:16.480
我建议  你去别处
I suggest that you continue your research

16:16.490 --> 16:19.790
继续研究
Elsewhere.

16:27.290 --> 16:30.050
如果是不小心
If you drop something

16:30.060 --> 16:32.780
落下的东西
By accident,

16:32.790 --> 16:35.160
上面肯定会有指纹
You leave a fingerprint on it.

16:35.820 --> 16:37.880
她就想让你发现这个
She wanted you to find this.

