-为什么  -你以前看过吗
Why? you ever seen it before?

16:39.790 --> 16:41.610
没有
No.

16:41.620 --> 16:42.610
你还记得
Do you remember

16:42.620 --> 16:43.810
那天的事吗
Anything about that day?

16:43.820 --> 16:45.290
我当时4岁
I was four years old.

16:46.760 --> 16:48.250
记得在哪拍的吗
Any idea where it was taken?

16:48.260 --> 16:51.260
忘了
No.

16:53.490 --> 16:56.250
没事吧
You okay?

16:56.260 --> 16:58.350
-如果我发现我妈妈  -听着
I mean, if i found out my mom was... listen,

16:58.360 --> 17:00.080
就我而言  她不是我妈
As far as i'm concerned, she's not my mom.

17:00.090 --> 17:01.450
只是我自由路上的绊脚石
She's just someone in the way of my freedom.

17:01.460 --> 17:02.820
懂了吗
All right?

17:11.420 --> 17:13.510
我6岁生日时
So, on my sixth birthday,

17:13.520 --> 17:17.550
爸爸已经离开很长时间了
Um, my father was long gone by then,

17:17.560 --> 17:19.850
只剩下我  妈妈   林肯
So it was just me, mom, and linc, and...

17:19.860 --> 17:21.510
妈妈送给我礼物
Mom hands me my present--

17:21.520 --> 17:24.550
我唯一的礼物  我以为...
My, uh, my only present-- and i just know...

17:24.560 --> 17:28.180
我猜那是千年隼号的模型
I just know it's the millennium falcon.

17:28.190 --> 17:29.850
有战斗警报声的吗
With the battle alert sound?

17:29.860 --> 17:30.950
没错
Exactly.

17:30.960 --> 17:32.950
-我有过一样的  -当然
-I totally owned that. -of course you did.

17:32.960 --> 17:35.350
我为这个求了母亲好几个礼拜
Anyway, i had been asking for this thing for weeks,

17:35.360 --> 17:37.510
包装的大小看起来一模一样
And the package is just the right size, and...

17:37.520 --> 17:38.950
我撕下包装
I rip open the wrapping paper

17:38.960 --> 17:42.710
结果却是个鸟巢
And... it's a birdhouse.

17:42.720 --> 17:43.980
不
Oh, no.

17:43.990 --> 17:46.650
其实不算是个鸟巢
Oh, yeah, except it's not even a birdhouse.

17:46.660 --> 17:48.510
是一套鸟巢玩具包
It's actually a birdhouse kit.

17:48.520 --> 17:50.650
真是遗憾
I'm so sorry.

17:50.660 --> 17:54.410
之后两天我都没和她说话
I didn't talk to her for two days after that,

17:54.420 --> 17:57.580
但她最后还是想办法让我开始拼
But when she finally got me to open the thing,

17:57.590 --> 17:59.010
我们坐在一起
We sat there together,

17:59.020 --> 18:00.950
一块一块的拼起来
Put it together piece by piece,

18:00.960 --> 18:03.220
那是我的第一个建筑作品
And it was the first thing i ever built.

18:05.090 --> 18:08.210
我很喜欢它
And i loved it...

18:08.220 --> 18:10.550
她一早就知道我会喜欢上它
And she knew i would.

18:10.560 --> 18:12.910
她比我更加了解我自己
She knew me better than i knew myself.

18:12.920 --> 18:14.850
母亲的天性
That's what moms do.

18:14.860 --> 18:17.550
奇怪的是
Yeah, but the strange thing is...

18:17.560 --> 18:19.410
即使我们有23年没见
Even though i haven't seen her for 23 years,

18:19.420 --> 18:20.480
我仍然能感觉到
There's this part of me

18:20.490 --> 18:25.320
她依然是如此
That feels like maybe she still does.

18:59.590 --> 19:02.480
你的车好像有些超载
Your truck looks a little low to the ground.

19:02.490 --> 19:03.480
介意下车来看看吗
You mind stepping outside?

19:03.490 --> 19:05.580
我刚刚才在20英里外磅重过
I just got weighed 20 miles back.

19:05.590 --> 19:08.420
你是高速公路巡警吗
You highway patrol?

19:10.360 --> 19:12.760
去哪里
Where are you going?

19:24.920 --> 19:26.610
这和你无关
You've got no business in there.

19:26.620 --> 19:27.750
除非你有搜查令
Unless you show me a warrant,

19:27.760 --> 19:30.160
否则马上滚下来
You get the hell out of there right now.

19:40.990 --> 19:42.420
谢谢
Thank you.

19:45.690 --> 19:47.650
上帝
Goodness.

19:47.660 --> 19:49.680
我有磅重点的票据
I got my weigh station ticket

19:49.690 --> 19:51.350
就在我的车上
Right here on the dash.

19:51.360 --> 19:53.420
给你看看
As soon as you see that...

19:54.460 --> 19:56.420
我刚刚才磅过重的
You'll see i got it right here.

19:58.820 --> 20:01.320
给
Here you go.

20:02.960 --> 20:05.350
我要你跟着我回凤凰城
I need you to follow me back to phoenix.

20:05.360 --> 20:06.910
你疯了吗
Are you crazy?

20:06.920 --> 20:08.550
我要去达拉斯卸货
I got to get this load to dallas.

20:08.560 --> 20:11.090
这是你自己选的
Well, that's your choice.

20:24.360 --> 20:27.620
找到他们了
I got 'em.

20:36.060 --> 20:39.210
我们该给你哥哥打电话
I think we need to call your brother.

20:39.220 --> 20:40.980
没信号
No signal.

20:40.990 --> 20:42.640
我们肯定在鸟不生蛋的地方
We must be in the middle of nowhere.

20:42.650 --> 20:45.780
林肯说如果公司抓到你的话
Lincoln said that if the company caught you...

20:48.760 --> 20:51.250
我看到这里有个侧门
I think i saw a side door back here.

20:51.260 --> 20:53.250
为何不走正门
What about the main door?

20:53.260 --> 20:54.510
不可能打开了
You'll never get that open.

20:54.520 --> 20:56.410
肯定从外面锁上了
I'm sure it's latched from the outside.

20:56.420 --> 20:57.940
侧门能开吗
Can you open the side door?

20:57.950 --> 21:00.860
也许
Maybe.

21:06.120 --> 21:08.650
莎拉
Sara.

21:08.660 --> 21:10.060
帮我一下
Help me out.

21:15.560 --> 21:18.120
我们搬不动这个
I don't think we're going to be able to move this.

21:22.020 --> 21:24.840
我们不用搬
Maybe we won't have to.

21:24.850 --> 21:27.780
我有个关于克兰兹将军的坏消息
I have troubling news about general krantz.

21:27.790 --> 21:29.180
他还活着
He's alive.

21:29.190 --> 21:31.080
这不可能
I don't see how that's possible.

21:31.090 --> 21:32.680
但我听说有一架
Yes, well, what i'm hearing is a

21:32.690 --> 21:34.280
从公司洛城总部起飞的
helicopter with

21:34.290 --> 21:38.080
直升飞机在一小时前
From company headquarters in los angeles one hour ago.

21:38.090 --> 21:40.280
抵达郊区峡谷
It landed for two minutes in canyon country

21:40.290 --> 21:42.550
正在返回洛城途中
And now it's back in los angeles.

21:42.560 --> 21:43.880
你找到他的尸体了吗
So you got the corpse?

21:43.890 --> 21:46.910
直升机降落在公司总部
The helicopter landed back at company headquarters.

21:46.920 --> 21:49.150
你知道除掉他对我们努力
You know how important getting rid of him is

21:49.160 --> 21:51.010
达到的目标有多重要
To what we're trying to accomplish.

21:51.020 --> 21:53.310
好吧  我可以搞定
All right, I can still get this done.

21:53.320 --> 21:56.020
时间不够了
Not in our time frame.

22:00.090 --> 22:01.750
好吧  我要速战速决
All right, I'm pulling the plug.

22:01.760 --> 22:04.110
我们要着手处理结果了
We need to start dealing with the consequences.

22:04.120 --> 22:05.850
等会儿  关键的是
Wait, wait, wait. first things first.

22:05.860 --> 22:07.250
他知道我已经背叛了他
He knows that i've betrayed him.

22:07.260 --> 22:08.350
我需要消失
I need to disappear.

22:08.360 --> 22:10.550
直觉真敏锐
I think that's a good instinct.

22:10.560 --> 22:12.610
我在森瓦利有间房子
I have a house in Sun Valley.

22:12.620 --> 22:15.010
我还有个主意
I have another idea.

22:15.020 --> 22:17.760
你介意打开扬声器吗
Do you mind putting me on speaker?

22:19.720 --> 22:22.650
格里夫  你是个勇敢的人
You know, Griff, you're a brave man.

22:22.660 --> 22:25.450
我感谢你为我做的每一件事
And I thank you for everything you've done.

22:25.460 --> 22:28.410
这是你的荣耀
It's been an honor.

22:28.420 --> 22:29.980
现在
Now.

22:29.990 --> 22:31.490
现在什么
"Now" what?

22:35.190 --> 22:37.810
照片里的汽车是佛罗里达的牌照
The car in this picture has Florida plates.

22:37.820 --> 22:39.210
你去那儿度过假吗
Did you ever vacation there?

22:39.220 --> 22:40.910
-没有  -你认不认识
