我们没有拍过
We didn't.

22:51.290 --> 22:52.680
照片被修改过了
It's been doctored.

22:52.690 --> 22:53.880
这一点我不能肯定
I'm not sure about that.

22:53.890 --> 22:57.340
光线  影子 都处理地很好
I mean, the lighting, the shadows, All sync up perfectly.

22:57.350 --> 22:59.880
这是78年版的西风
This is a '78 zephyr.

22:59.890 --> 23:02.650
迈克尔76年出生
Michael was born in '76.

23:04.290 --> 23:06.980
你是唯一能想起来的人
You're the only one who could've picked up on that.

23:06.990 --> 23:08.880
这照片是特意为你修改的
She doctored that for you.

23:08.890 --> 23:10.680
看看她还可能修改了什么
Let's see what else she might've changed.

23:10.690 --> 23:12.640
那辆西风的牌照是什么
What's the license plate on that zephyr?

23:12.650 --> 23:16.480
M-I-K 4-4-1
M-I-K 4-4-1.

23:16.490 --> 23:19.140
马丁路德金大道与411道路交叉口处
Martin Luther King boulevard intersects with route 441

23:19.150 --> 23:20.640
大概离这里偏北五英里
About five miles north of here.

23:20.650 --> 23:21.980
很好
Good.

23:21.990 --> 23:23.980
你们在这里  我们在小哈瓦那
You guys are here. listen, we're a little outmanned

23:23.990 --> 23:25.840
人手不够  你们可以支援我们
Down in Little Havana. we could use some backup.

23:25.850 --> 23:27.780
我们有买家的线索
We got a lead on the buyer.

23:27.790 --> 23:29.920
很好  那我们还等什么
Great, what are we waiting for?

23:30.040 --> 23:31.740
我还是自己干吧
I think I gonna do it myself.

23:31.820 --> 23:33.680
我们应该在一起  团队合作嘛
Come on, let's stay together. we're a team, right?

23:33.690 --> 23:35.710
-我说过我能做到  -经过今早的
- I said i got it.  - After our little

23:35.720 --> 23:37.240
小小特殊快递
Special deliveries this morning,

23:37.250 --> 23:38.740
每个人都是平等的了
Each one of us has an equal stake.

23:38.750 --> 23:41.690
无论谁牵的头  我们都要让他们出局
Whoever started this, we're all going to take them out.

23:44.850 --> 23:47.610
我们认为买家是林肯的母亲
The buyer, we think it's Lincoln's mother.

23:47.620 --> 23:49.040
你说什么
What?

23:49.050 --> 23:51.190
正如我所说  我自己干
Like i said, i'm doing this myself.

23:51.950 --> 23:53.040
林肯
Linc!

23:53.050 --> 23:54.910
如果她有"锡拉"
If she has scylla,

23:54.920 --> 23:56.540
