She's not just going to hand it over

23:56.550 --> 23:58.380
与将军相比是有过之而无不及
Any more than the general would have.

23:58.390 --> 23:59.580
你也不知道
You don't know that.

23:59.590 --> 24:01.280
我们都认为拿着"锡拉"的人
We always thought whoever had scylla

24:01.290 --> 24:02.640
会像将军那样做事
Would do what the general did.

24:02.650 --> 24:04.040
也许她不会
Maybe she won't.

24:04.050 --> 24:05.140
你当真吗
Are you serious?

24:05.150 --> 24:06.980
你妈是公司特工
Your mother is a company agent?

24:06.990 --> 24:08.410
她曾经是
She was.

24:08.420 --> 24:09.780
她现在可能是个好人了
She might be one of the good guys now.

24:09.790 --> 24:11.140
恕我直言
With all due respect,

24:11.150 --> 24:12.780
我觉得你没有把握
I don't think you're in a place where you can make

24:12.790 --> 24:14.410
断定这点
A clear determination about that.

24:14.420 --> 24:17.540
这个MLK 441可能什么也不是
Listen, this MLK 441 could be nothing.

24:17.550 --> 24:18.610
但在那座教堂里
But at the church,

24:18.620 --> 24:20.120
可能会有"锡拉"
There could be scylla.

24:21.490 --> 24:23.250
如果需要你帮助  我会打电话
If i need you, i'll call.

24:24.950 --> 24:27.290
这应该管用
This should work.

24:51.950 --> 24:53.940
克里斯汀娜
Christina?

24:53.950 --> 24:55.570
你有必要知道在过去24小时中
You need to acknowledge that our chance

24:55.580 --> 24:58.240
我们成功的几率大大降低了
Of success has substantially declined in the last 24 hours.

24:58.250 --> 24:59.940
有人在追查我们
There are people out looking for us.

24:59.950 --> 25:02.140
要开始考虑退路了
We need to start thinking in terms of contingencies.

25:02.150 --> 25:04.940
再等等  就几天
Just a little while longer, only a few more days.

25:04.950 --> 25:06.810
克兰兹将军面对严重威胁时
General Krantz refused to adjust

25:06.820 --> 25:08.470
也拒绝调整
When there were credible threats against him.

25:08.480 --> 25:10.880
所以我们才夺取"锡拉"
That's the reason we have scylla now.

25:11.890 --> 25:15.850
你不会拿我和他相提并论吧
Are you honestly comparing me to him?

25:16.890 --> 25:21.440
我知道在整件事中你给自己的定位
I understand what you think your role is in all of this,

25:21.450 --> 25:23.080
也很感谢你的努力
And I appreciate your efforts.

25:23.090 --> 25:24.540
但如果你觉得
But if you can't tell the difference

25:24.550 --> 25:26.540
我和他一样  你就去找将军
Between he and I, perhaps you need to ask

25:26.550 --> 25:29.320
要回你的职位
The general for your old job back.

25:32.090 --> 25:33.940
瞧
Oh, look.

25:33.950 --> 25:37.720
是他打的  你想接吗
Here he is. would you like to take the call?

25:41.850 --> 25:43.440
乔纳森
Jonathan.

25:43.450 --> 25:45.040
