She'll listen to me.

41:56.120 --> 41:57.610
她叫你不要回去了  林肯
She asked you not to come back, Linc.

41:57.620 --> 41:59.020
这就是警告
That's a warning.

42:35.350 --> 42:38.220
林肯回广场了
Lincoln's back at the plaza.

42:39.190 --> 42:40.840
我觉得我们必须
I think we need

42:40.850 --> 42:42.280
认识到他比我们
To realize he's more of a threat

42:42.290 --> 42:43.540
设想中更具威胁
Than we gave him credit for.

42:43.550 --> 42:44.940
他找到那栋大厦了
He found the mansion.

42:44.950 --> 42:46.680
他的人在教堂找到了藏匿物
His guys got the stash at the church.

42:46.690 --> 42:47.910
他不会收手的
He's not going to stop.

42:47.920 --> 42:51.320
我告诉过他不要搅和的
I told him to stay away.

43:03.150 --> 43:04.380
克里斯汀娜
Christina,

43:04.390 --> 43:06.750
我们正待命击毙
We have a clean shot.

43:17.690 --> 43:19.710
击毙
Take it.

43:19.720 --> 43:21.150
击毙
Take it.
